56
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:17,082
I'm not going to the hotel, I'll help search.

57
00:04:17,082 --> 00:04:18,456
All right.

58
00:04:18,456 --> 00:04:21,696
Gu Mingze, you're a bit older, keep an eye on him.

59
00:04:21,696 --> 00:04:23,960
