137
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:07,630
Dad.

138
00:10:07,630 --> 00:10:09,470
 Did you find your sister? 

139
00:10:09,470 --> 00:10:11,960
Don't worry, we found her.

140
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:14,280
