144
00:10:41,590 --> 00:10:42,870
 Go ahead and change your clothes first. 

145
00:10:42,870 --> 00:10:45,080
 I grabbed these from your bag while you were out searching. 

146
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:47,330
 They're clean. Don't catch a cold. 

147
00:10:55,560 --> 00:10:57,870
- Your ankle's swollen! 
 - I'm okay.

148
00:10:57,870 --> 00:10:59,890
Sir, here's what you asked for.

149
00:11:01,230 --> 00:11:03,860
You're hopeless with this. Let me do it.

150
00:11:06,350 --> 00:11:08,080
Xuejiao, talk about bad luck.

151
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:10,910
You got lost in the rain, and it stopped the second you got back.

152
00:11:10,910 --> 00:11:13,780
It's a pity that Senior Brother Lin spent so much effort setting up that tent.

153
00:11:19,040 --> 00:11:20,960
Here, I got rooms for you.

154
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:23,470
- Go take a shower. 
 - Thank you, Senior Brother Lin.

155
00:11:23,470 --> 00:11:26,490
Maybe I should book you a nicer suite.

156
00:11:30,590 --> 00:11:32,920
Wait til you're making your own money.

157
