158
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:36,200
Hello, Dr. Cai?

159
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:38,290
Aren't you also a student, too?

160
00:11:41,110 --> 00:11:42,560
Too cold?

161
00:11:42,560 --> 00:11:44,020
No, it's fine.

162
00:12:03,680 --> 00:12:05,260
Shiyun!

163
00:12:05,260 --> 00:12:06,910
Shiyun!

164
00:12:08,470 --> 00:12:10,730
Let's head back.

165
00:12:10,730 --> 00:12:12,850
You told me to leave, remember?

166
00:12:12,850 --> 00:12:14,420
Stop it. It's dark and the road's slippery.

167
00:12:14,420 --> 00:12:15,730
What if you get hurt?

168
00:12:15,730 --> 00:12:17,700
Don't worry about me!

169
00:12:17,700 --> 00:12:20,180
I said to leave me alone!

170
00:12:22,560 --> 00:12:23,590
Let go!

171
00:12:23,590 --> 00:12:24,940
You...

172
00:12:24,940 --> 00:12:26,960
Gu Mingze!

173
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:28,320
Gu Mingze!

174
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,451
Put me down!

175
00:12:29,451 --> 00:12:31,280
Let me go!

176
00:12:31,280 --> 00:12:32,870
Put me down!

177
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:55,720
   

178
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:01,530
Sorry, sir.

179
00:13:01,530 --> 00:13:03,005
If the room is locked from inside,

180
00:13:03,005 --> 00:13:05,700
we can't open it unless there's a fire.

181
00:13:05,700 --> 00:13:08,360
Well, just book me another room.

182
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:10,100
I really need a shower.

183
00:13:10,100 --> 00:13:13,220
I'll need your ID, please.

184
00:13:14,220 --> 00:13:17,080
My ID is in that locked room.

185
00:13:23,340 --> 00:13:24,940
Senior Brother Lin!

186
00:13:24,940 --> 00:13:26,890
Senior Brother Lin!

187
00:13:26,890 --> 00:13:28,440
Thank you.

188
00:13:31,940 --> 00:13:36,630
This is Gu Mingze's card, use his room to take a shower and get some rest.

189
00:13:37,300 --> 00:13:38,770
Thanks.

190
00:13:38,770 --> 00:13:40,180
Here, this is for you.

191
00:13:40,180 --> 00:13:41,120
Huh?

192
00:13:41,120 --> 00:13:42,490
Just take it.

193
00:13:42,490 --> 00:13:44,080
We found Xuejiao all thanks to you.

194
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,820
You earned it.

195
00:13:47,610 --> 00:13:51,400
I'll grab these to cheer Xuejiao up.

196
00:13:58,890 --> 00:14:00,590
Thanks.

197
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:17,630
Shiyun, it's getting late.

198
00:14:17,630 --> 00:14:21,100
Do you want to head back?

199
00:14:21,100 --> 00:14:22,720
I'd rather just go home.

200
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:24,880
Okay, forget it.

201
00:14:24,880 --> 00:14:27,200
I'm with you wherever you want to go.

202
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:30,610
How about I just take you home?

203
00:14:33,630 --> 00:14:35,490
Home?

204
00:14:36,430 --> 00:14:37,940
No.

205
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:40,670
I don't want to go back there either.

206
00:14:40,670 --> 00:14:43,840
I'd rather just be sitting here alone.

207
00:14:51,980 --> 00:14:56,720
You know, Xuejiao told us

208
00:14:56,720 --> 00:14:59,300
that you didn't mean it.

209
00:15:04,750 --> 00:15:06,610
Shiyun,

210
00:15:06,610 --> 00:15:10,220
everyone makes mistakes sometimes.

211
00:15:10,220 --> 00:15:13,180
Why not just apologize to Xuejiao?

212
00:15:13,180 --> 00:15:14,490
She'll forgive you, for sure.

213
00:15:14,490 --> 00:15:15,820
No!

214
00:15:15,820 --> 00:15:17,960
I don't need her playing the saint.

215
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:20,530
I don't need it! I meant what I did!

216
00:15:20,530 --> 00:15:22,230
I saw her heading the wrong way, and I let her!

217
00:15:22,230 --> 00:15:24,080
I'm a terrible person!

218
00:15:32,340 --> 00:15:34,350
But...

219
00:15:34,350 --> 00:15:36,370
But why?

220
00:15:36,370 --> 00:15:38,910
You and Xuejiao used to be so close.

221
00:15:38,910 --> 00:15:41,730
You two were inseparable, like you shared everything.

222
00:15:41,730 --> 00:15:46,610
How did things get this ugly,

223
00:15:48,010 --> 00:15:50,350
all of a sudden?

224
00:15:59,100 --> 00:16:01,360
Do you want the truth?

225
00:16:11,340 --> 00:16:13,010
I...

226
00:16:13,010 --> 00:16:14,830
I'm jealous of her.

227
00:16:15,560 --> 00:16:17,510
I always have been,

228
00:16:17,948 --> 00:16:20,474
since we were kids.

229
00:16:20,474 --> 00:16:23,604
So jealous it was eating me up inside.

230
00:16:27,640 --> 00:16:29,290
You?

231
00:16:29,995 --> 00:16:32,045
Jealous of her?

232
00:16:40,745 --> 00:16:44,045
Wait, is it because of me?

233
00:16:48,905 --> 00:16:49,980
Is it because of me?

234
00:16:49,980 --> 00:16:51,830
You?

235
00:16:53,505 --> 00:16:55,445
So it is because of me...

236
00:16:56,453 --> 00:16:58,013
No.

237
00:16:58,735 --> 00:17:00,145
Gu Mingze, are you nuts?

238
00:17:00,145 --> 00:17:02,585
