246
00:17:54,305 --> 00:17:55,745
I'll go find you something to eat.

247
00:17:55,745 --> 00:17:58,195
Come on, you're the hungry one.

248
00:18:38,675 --> 00:18:40,855
Gu Mingze! Where'd you get that bread?

249
00:18:40,855 --> 00:18:42,675
