250
00:18:42,675 --> 00:18:44,105
You...

251
00:18:45,475 --> 00:18:47,175
Hang on a sec.

252
00:18:59,065 --> 00:19:00,265
Wait, what?

253
00:19:00,265 --> 00:19:02,355
Why is it a sad face?

254
00:19:13,245 --> 00:19:15,405
See? Now it looks like a smile.

255
00:19:15,405 --> 00:19:16,539
That's ugly!

256
00:19:16,539 --> 00:19:18,189
No thanks.

257
00:19:20,965 --> 00:19:22,395
That's more like it.

258
00:19:22,395 --> 00:19:26,645
If you don't like someone, be straight with them.

259
00:19:26,645 --> 00:19:29,895
If you like someone, own up.

260
00:19:29,895 --> 00:19:31,815
Just be honest, like you said.

261
00:19:31,815 --> 00:19:33,395
This is who you are.

262
00:19:33,395 --> 00:19:34,855
If they accept you, that's great.

263
00:19:34,855 --> 00:19:37,439
If not? It's their loss.

264
00:19:37,439 --> 00:19:41,719
Someone will love the real you eventually.

