00:19:56,630 --> 00:19:58,197
Nothing.

267
00:19:58,197 --> 00:20:00,447
I just realized...

268
00:20:02,519 --> 00:20:06,499
you're not as clueless as I thought you were.

269
00:20:10,580 --> 00:20:12,100
Wait!

270
00:20:12,100 --> 00:20:14,900
