271
00:20:14,900 --> 00:20:16,410
Zhou Shiyun, be honest with me.

272
00:20:16,410 --> 00:20:17,690
Not that much.

273
00:20:17,690 --> 00:20:19,390
Be nice!

274
00:20:20,490 --> 00:20:23,070
- Tell me or I'll smear this on your face! 
 - Seriously, not that clueless!

275
00:20:23,070 --> 00:20:25,010
Just a tiny bit.

276
00:20:25,010 --> 00:20:26,590
A tiny bit? That won't do!

277
00:20:26,590 --> 00:20:27,620
I'm super smart.

278
00:20:27,620 --> 00:20:29,510
- Put down the bread first! 
 - Honestly, I feel like a genius.

279
00:20:29,510 --> 00:20:31,240
No! Stop!

280
00:20:31,240 --> 00:20:32,870
This is for you anyway!

281
00:20:32,870 --> 00:20:34,490
No!

282
00:20:37,300 --> 00:20:40,300
