284
00:20:42,580 --> 00:20:44,450
Do you have a problem with instant noodles?

285
00:20:44,450 --> 00:20:47,820
It's got everything. Broth, greens, meat, noodles.

286
00:20:47,820 --> 00:20:49,790
A perfectly balanced meal!

287
00:20:49,790 --> 00:20:51,540
It could use more meat.

288
00:20:51,540 --> 00:20:53,840
So, is it good or not?

289
00:20:58,240 --> 00:20:59,960
Amazing.

290
00:20:59,960 --> 00:21:01,930
Warming me up from the inside.

291
00:21:01,930 --> 00:21:05,140
I was freezing just now, and all I craved was this.

292
00:21:05,140 --> 00:21:07,050
I understand you best, right?

293
00:21:11,590 --> 00:21:13,540
Excuse me, are you Ms. Gu Xuejiao?

294
00:21:13,540 --> 00:21:14,930
I am.

295
00:21:14,930 --> 00:21:17,010
Mr. Lin bought these meds for you.

296
00:21:17,010 --> 00:21:20,320
He's busy now, but asked me to deliver them as soon as I see you.

297
00:21:20,320 --> 00:21:21,550
- Thank you. 
 - You're welcome.

298
00:21:21,550 --> 00:21:22,980
Thanks.

299
00:21:25,110 --> 00:21:26,920
Take a look.

300
00:21:28,070 --> 00:21:30,520
He thought of everything.

301
00:21:34,030 --> 00:21:36,650
Older guys are so thoughtful, huh?

302
00:21:36,650 --> 00:21:39,410
Not only meds, he even remembered chocolate.

303
00:21:39,410 --> 00:21:43,760
Unlike Yi Tianyu, his ice pack felt like a weapon ready to kill.

304
00:21:51,400 --> 00:21:54,500
You know, Senior Brother Lin literally carried you back today.

305
00:21:55,471 --> 00:21:58,213
Were you nervous?

306
00:21:58,213 --> 00:22:00,113
Why would I be nervous?

307
00:22:00,113 --> 00:22:01,334
No big deal at all.

308
00:22:01,334 --> 00:22:03,200
Nothing to be nervous about.

309
00:22:03,200 --> 00:22:05,167
Come on, be honest. Okay?

310
00:22:05,167 --> 00:22:07,160
Check your phone. You got a lot of texts.

311
00:22:07,160 --> 00:22:09,190
Did something happen?

312
00:22:14,960 --> 00:22:19,300
Qi Lei just said in the group chat that his school just dropped the cutoff scores!

313
00:22:22,000 --> 00:22:22,970
What about Jinghai University?

314
00:22:22,970 --> 00:22:24,830
Let me check.

315
00:22:24,830 --> 00:22:26,970
Jinghai...

316
00:22:26,970 --> 00:22:28,680
Not yet.

317
00:22:28,680 --> 00:22:31,270
Ugh, why can't they release their scores all at once?

318
00:22:31,270 --> 00:22:34,840
This waiting game is torture.

319
00:22:36,140 --> 00:22:40,970
Right, my throat's parched from stress.

320
00:22:40,970 --> 00:22:43,140
Tiantian, I could use an ice-cold cola.

321
00:22:43,140 --> 00:22:44,940
Let's go grab one.

322
00:22:45,790 --> 00:22:47,750
Cola can wait.

323
00:22:47,750 --> 00:22:49,720
I've got something urgent to deal with.

324
00:22:49,720 --> 00:22:51,990
I have to run to my room.

325
00:22:52,880 --> 00:22:56,920
These are the replacement keys for Gu Mingze and Zhou Shiyun. Make sure they get these.

326
00:22:56,920 --> 00:22:58,400
Here's yours and mine.

327
00:22:58,400 --> 00:22:59,380
I'm heading up.

328
00:22:59,380 --> 00:23:00,710
Okay.

329
00:23:10,640 --> 00:23:11,720
Hey, Mom.

330
00:23:11,720 --> 00:23:15,560
 Xuejiao, Jinghai University just dropped their cutoff scores! 

331
00:23:26,480 --> 00:23:30,820
 Sun Tiantian, you hid such a large stash of snacks 

332
00:23:30,820 --> 00:23:33,280
and all you fed me was instant noodles?

333
00:23:35,534 --> 00:23:37,484
Oh, showering?

334
00:23:38,750 --> 00:23:40,380
 I'm still starving. 

335
00:23:40,380 --> 00:23:42,100
 How's the shower? 

336
00:23:42,100 --> 00:23:44,060
 Mind if I come in to wash my hands? 

337
00:23:44,060 --> 00:23:46,180
 I want to eat a bit more. 

338
00:23:52,350 --> 00:23:54,360
 You locked the door? 

339
00:23:54,968 --> 00:23:56,878
You treat me like an outsider.

340
00:24:01,750 --> 00:24:04,400
I'm so happy right now. I can't hold it in!

341
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:05,672
Let me just say this...

342
00:24:05,672 --> 00:24:08,800
I was going to tell Senior Brother Lin first.

343
00:24:10,450 --> 00:24:13,030
My dream came true.

344
00:24:13,030 --> 00:24:16,600
I got into Jinghai University!

345
00:24:22,650 --> 00:24:23,830
Screw everything else right now,

346
00:24:23,830 --> 00:24:25,270
I just want an ice-cold cola.

347
00:24:25,270 --> 00:24:26,250
Hurry up and finish your shower

348
00:24:26,250 --> 00:24:28,200
so we can go and get one together.

349
00:24:28,200 --> 00:24:30,550
Actually, never mind, I'll call Senior Brother Lin real quick

350
00:24:30,550 --> 00:24:32,660
and share the good news with him.

351
00:24:38,270 --> 00:24:40,960
 Sorry, the subscriber you dialed is powered off. 

352
00:24:40,960 --> 00:24:44,600
 Sorry, the subscriber you dialed is powered off. 

353
00:24:45,440 --> 00:24:47,900
He must be busy, I guess.

354
00:24:47,900 --> 00:24:55,140
Tiantian, earlier you asked if I was nervous. Right?

355
00:25:02,960 --> 00:25:05,010
The truth is,

356
00:25:05,010 --> 00:25:08,380
the moment I saw him in the woods earlier,

357
00:25:08,380 --> 00:25:13,420
 I really hoped I'd keep seeing him in college. 

358
00:25:18,830 --> 00:25:20,540
Tiantian?

359
00:25:20,540 --> 00:25:22,720
 Why are you so quiet? 

360
00:25:30,200 --> 00:25:31,860
 Tiantian? 

361
00:25:31,860 --> 00:25:33,510
Are you okay in there?

362
00:25:33,510 --> 00:25:34,860
 Tiantian? 

363
00:25:34,860 --> 00:25:36,880
Did you pass out?

364
00:25:36,880 --> 00:25:39,200
 Say something or I'm breaking in! 

365
00:25:39,200 --> 00:25:40,900
Tiantian!

366
00:25:45,720 --> 00:25:48,450
W-Why are you here?

367
00:25:51,160 --> 00:25:53,400
This is Gu Mingze's room.

368
00:25:53,400 --> 00:25:57,570
You got lost, right?

369
00:26:00,440 --> 00:26:02,760
Well, enjoy your shower. Bye.

370
00:26:13,451 --> 00:26:15,560
Tiantian.

371
00:26:15,560 --> 00:26:19,790
How was I supposed to know Senior Brother Lin was showering?

372
00:26:19,790 --> 00:26:21,500
Relax, don't worry.

373
00:26:21,500 --> 00:26:25,670
It's my fault, I bolted too fast and messed up the keys.

374
00:26:26,906 --> 00:26:30,617
You were the first person I wanted to share my good news with,

375
00:26:30,617 --> 00:26:32,437
and you set me up like this?

376
00:26:34,030 --> 00:26:36,780
So, how was the view?

377
00:26:39,160 --> 00:26:40,640
 This is Gu Mingze's room. 

378
00:26:40,640 --> 00:26:42,173
- Looks like... 
 - He...

379
00:26:42,173 --> 00:26:43,820
 You got lost, right? 

380
00:26:43,820 --> 00:26:45,450
I didn't see anything!

381
00:26:45,450 --> 00:26:47,285
Come on, you totally did.

382
00:26:47,285 --> 00:26:48,860
- No, I really didn't. 
 - You definitely did!

383
00:26:48,860 --> 00:26:50,240
That's your guilty face!

384
00:26:50,240 --> 00:26:51,770
I can always tell when you lie.

385
00:26:51,770 --> 00:26:53,720
- I swear, I didn't see a thing. 
 - Come on, tell me!

386
00:26:53,720 --> 00:26:55,380
Eight-pack abs?

387
00:26:56,500 --> 00:26:58,180
Six-pack? Right?

388
00:26:58,180 --> 00:26:59,870
Six or eight, did you count? Did you?

389
00:26:59,870 --> 00:27:01,885
- Just one! 
 - Did you count?

390
00:27:01,885 --> 00:27:03,716
- No way... 
 - I really didn't see!

391
00:27:03,716 --> 00:27:05,646
You totally did!

392
00:27:11,970 --> 00:27:13,720
 Xuejiao, 

393
00:27:13,720 --> 00:27:17,350
 first, my apologies for today's mishap. 

394
00:27:18,080 --> 00:27:20,750
 But weirdly, that made me the first person you shared your good news 

395
00:27:20,750 --> 00:27:24,650
 about getting into Jinghai University. 

396
00:27:24,650 --> 00:27:26,320
Dr. Cai, take a look.

397
00:27:26,320 --> 00:27:30,360
  The Least I can do is get you this ice-cold coke. 

398
00:27:30,360 --> 00:27:35,470
 And lastly, I wish you all the best at Jinghai University. 

399
00:27:35,470 --> 00:27:37,310
 Lin Zhihua. 

400
00:27:37,310 --> 00:27:39,520
   

401
00:27:46,680 --> 00:27:50,030
 Why couldn't you get into Jinghai University like Gu Xuejiao? 

402
00:27:50,030 --> 00:27:52,300
 You're such a disappointment. 

403
00:27:52,300 --> 00:27:54,121
 All three years of high school, 

404
00:27:54,121 --> 00:27:57,260
 - think about how much time and money I spent on you.  
 - Shiyun?

405
00:27:57,260 --> 00:27:59,310
 Go ahead, do the math for me. 

406
00:27:59,310 --> 00:28:01,400
 Is this how you thank me? 
   

407
00:28:01,400 --> 00:28:04,200
 My daughter lost to Li Sitong's daughter! 

408
00:28:04,200 --> 00:28:06,130
 Do you know how humiliating that is? 

409
00:28:06,130 --> 00:28:09,160
 How am I supposed to hold my head up in front of others? 

410
00:28:09,160 --> 00:28:11,370
 What good are you anyway? 

411
00:28:11,370 --> 00:28:14,530
 You're nothing but an embarrassment! 

412
00:28:16,040 --> 00:28:17,420
 Say something. 

413
00:28:17,420 --> 00:28:18,666
 What, now? 

414
00:28:18,666 --> 00:28:20,917
 You can't even make a sound? 

415
00:28:20,917 --> 00:28:22,708
Who cares about your pride?

416
00:28:22,708 --> 00:28:25,319
She's your daughter, not some trophy to show off!

417
00:28:25,319 --> 00:28:27,560
What's wrong with you?

418
00:28:27,560 --> 00:28:28,841
 What's wrong with you? 

419
00:28:28,841 --> 00:28:30,620
 Who do you think you are? 

420
00:28:30,620 --> 00:28:32,490
 Who are you to talk to me like that? 

421
00:28:32,490 --> 00:28:34,739
 Put Zhou Shiyun on! 

422
00:28:34,739 --> 00:28:38,180
I'm just someone who can't stand this crap.

423
00:28:38,180 --> 00:28:40,315
 Where is she? 
   

424
00:29:07,320 --> 00:29:08,830
Shiyun.

425
00:29:09,440 --> 00:29:11,320
So your mom...

426
00:29:11,889 --> 00:29:14,199
has always treated you like this?

427
00:29:15,019 --> 00:29:19,069
 After that day, none of us saw Zhou Shiyun again. 

428
00:29:19,069 --> 00:29:20,769
 Word is, she didn't get into her top choice school. 

429
00:29:20,769 --> 00:29:22,349
 Too many applied. 

430
00:29:22,349 --> 00:29:24,549
 Nobody knew where she ended up. 

431
00:29:24,549 --> 00:29:28,679
 For Auntie Wanjun, this must be the ultimate shame. 

432
00:29:29,635 --> 00:29:34,915
 Yi Tianyu got into JUFE thanks to his athletic skills. 

433
00:29:36,410 --> 00:29:39,171
 Sun Tiantian didn't bother repeating a year 

434
00:29:39,171 --> 00:29:40,830
 and started working as a pastry apprentice 

435
00:29:40,830 --> 00:29:43,870
 with her parents' support. 

436
00:29:43,874 --> 00:29:47,055
 Gu Mingze, unsurprisingly, also didn't get in. 

437
00:29:47,055 --> 00:29:49,200
 But over the summer, he gathered a team 

438
00:29:49,200 --> 00:29:53,231
 of like-minded people to create a Triple A game, 

439
00:29:53,231 --> 00:29:55,839
 forging a unique path for himself. 

440
00:29:55,839 --> 00:29:59,491
 Qi Lei headed off happily to a technical college out of town. 

441
00:29:59,491 --> 00:30:03,361
 And me, Gu Xuejiao, I'm going to Jinghai University! 

442
00:30:05,319 --> 00:30:06,789
Two.

443
00:30:10,009 --> 00:30:11,529
One.

444
00:30:18,209 --> 00:30:19,639
Two.

445
00:30:21,169 --> 00:30:22,899
Halt.

446
00:30:27,799 --> 00:30:29,889
Everyone. Eyes left!

447
00:30:29,889 --> 00:30:31,939
Pick up those feet! Move it!

448
00:30:35,349 --> 00:30:36,629
- What are you doing? 
 - Sorry.

449
00:30:36,629 --> 00:30:37,839
I couldn't stop!

450
00:30:37,839 --> 00:30:40,279
Blind or just uncoordinated?

451
00:30:42,839 --> 00:30:46,049
You still got energy to fight?

452
00:30:48,489 --> 00:30:51,769
Those who were talking, step forward!

453
00:30:54,219 --> 00:30:56,720
Don't make me ask twice.

454
00:30:56,720 --> 00:30:59,570
Otherwise, everyone here will be doing extra drills with you.

455
00:31:12,739 --> 00:31:13,789
All right.

456
00:31:13,789 --> 00:31:15,729
You four, stand at attention.

457
00:31:15,729 --> 00:31:17,489
So loyal!

458
00:31:17,489 --> 00:31:19,429
The rest of you, dismissed!

459
00:31:20,359 --> 00:31:22,179
Worst luck ever.

460
00:31:22,179 --> 00:31:25,309
Day one, and we're already doing double extra drills.

461
00:31:25,309 --> 00:31:27,059
Thanks to you.

462
00:31:28,873 --> 00:31:29,909
That's your own fault.

463
00:31:29,909 --> 00:31:32,109
What? You want to keep going?

464
00:31:32,109 --> 00:31:33,709
Attention!

465
00:31:35,119 --> 00:31:36,639
See you.

466
00:31:37,279 --> 00:31:38,769
Bye-bye.

467
00:31:44,829 --> 00:31:46,349
It's boiling out there.

468
00:31:46,349 --> 00:31:48,779
Finally made it back.

469
00:31:56,620 --> 00:31:59,810
Does this count as our first roommate dinner?

470
00:31:59,810 --> 00:32:01,760
Of course not. Once training's over,

471
00:32:01,760 --> 00:32:02,930
we're going out for a proper meal.

472
00:32:02,930 --> 00:32:04,500
I'm in.

473
00:32:08,680 --> 00:32:09,960
Why are you eating so little?

474
00:32:09,960 --> 00:32:11,930
Are you not worried about low blood sugar?

475
00:32:11,930 --> 00:32:13,370
Here, have a drumstick.

476
00:32:13,370 --> 00:32:15,170
I'm good.

477
00:32:16,200 --> 00:32:17,940
Thanks.

478
00:32:20,040 --> 00:32:22,040
What is that?

479
00:32:22,040 --> 00:32:24,320
Extra stinky snail rice noodles!

480
00:32:34,720 --> 00:32:36,850
Shu Lan, I'm so sorry.

481
00:32:36,850 --> 00:32:37,960
Stay away from me.

482
00:32:37,960 --> 00:32:40,830
New rule: no more smelly food in the dorm.

483
00:32:45,070 --> 00:32:48,480
The AC's on, why are you opening the window?

484
00:32:51,680 --> 00:32:53,480
Come on!

485
00:32:53,480 --> 00:32:55,170
It's so freaking hot.

486
00:32:55,170 --> 00:32:56,520
Please don't turn off the AC.

487
00:32:56,520 --> 00:32:57,610
I get cold easily, okay?

488
00:32:57,610 --> 00:32:59,280
It's 36 degrees out today.

489
00:32:59,280 --> 00:33:00,520
Are you sure you're cold?

490
00:33:00,520 --> 00:33:02,330
AC's bad for you.

491
00:33:02,330 --> 00:33:05,000
You'll get chilled to the bone.

492
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:06,720
Ever heard of that?

493
00:33:06,720 --> 00:33:08,000
Whatever.

494
00:33:08,000 --> 00:33:09,170
I'm fine.

495
00:33:09,170 --> 00:33:11,890
Don't you feel like this dorm is a giant steamer?

496
00:33:11,890 --> 00:33:14,490
We're just buns waiting to be cooked.

497
00:33:15,160 --> 00:33:19,640
You'll stop being cold when we're medium-rare.

498
00:33:19,640 --> 00:33:21,550
Today,

499
00:33:21,550 --> 00:33:24,160
I'm just going to skip the common sense for once.

500
00:33:24,160 --> 00:33:25,550
You guys don't believe me, huh?

501
00:33:25,550 --> 00:33:27,570
Fine, let's see some numbers.

502
00:33:28,400 --> 00:33:30,040
Check out these stats.

503
00:33:30,040 --> 00:33:33,430
Cities with AC have way more people with cold symptoms.

504
00:33:33,430 --> 00:33:34,718
Case closed.

505
00:33:34,718 --> 00:33:36,593
Numbers don't lie.

506
00:33:36,593 --> 00:33:39,373
So I'm telling you, no AC today.

507
00:33:46,240 --> 00:33:47,769
Save yourself the embarrassment.

508
00:33:47,769 --> 00:33:49,670
I won first in the math Olympiad,

509
00:33:49,670 --> 00:33:51,431
scored perfect on all my major math exams,

510
00:33:51,431 --> 00:33:53,891
even five of you combined couldn't out-calculate me.

511
00:33:57,550 --> 00:34:01,200
Just like you said, numbers don't lie.

512
00:34:01,200 --> 00:34:04,080
In every city, the figure on the left is lower than the one on the right,

513
00:34:04,080 --> 00:34:06,480
but when you look at the overall total, the left is actually higher.

514
00:34:06,480 --> 00:34:11,230
Which means your whole "AC makes you cold" theory is totally wrong.

515
00:34:11,230 --> 00:34:15,101
Yeah, Shu Lan, what if we just messed up the math?

516
00:34:15,101 --> 00:34:17,820
You're the math whiz, why don't you check?

517
00:34:17,820 --> 00:34:21,110
And besides, the sample sizes are all different.

518
00:34:21,110 --> 00:34:22,900
We don't know if they had any control variables.

519
00:34:22,900 --> 00:34:24,280
This data's basically useless.

520
00:34:24,280 --> 00:34:29,610
Shu Lan, math whiz or not, you can't just treat us like we're fools.

521
00:34:29,610 --> 00:34:32,650
I mean, we all got into Jinghai University,

522
00:34:32,650 --> 00:34:35,230
clearly we're not bad at math.

523
00:34:35,230 --> 00:34:37,600
Whatever. Run the AC if you want.

524
00:34:37,600 --> 00:34:40,691
Don't blame me if you get sick.

525
00:34:40,691 --> 00:34:43,066
No need, thanks for the warning.

526
00:34:43,880 --> 00:34:48,940
How about we crack the window for some fresh air?

527
00:34:48,940 --> 00:34:54,260
It'll help the air circulate, and we won't feel so stuffy.

528
00:34:54,260 --> 00:34:56,550
- Works for me. 
 - No problem.

529
00:35:03,150 --> 00:35:04,790
Whatever.

530
00:35:22,340 --> 00:35:24,841
Guess the internet wasn't kidding.

531
00:35:24,841 --> 00:35:29,380
